	(3659,531,'home_sections_0_section_content','FourPoint Energy is a private exploration and production company founded by the leadership team of Cordillera Energy Partners following the sale to Apache Corporation in 2012. FourPoint Energy is headquartered in Denver, Colorado. Building on over 30 years of experience this fourth enterprise will be centered around the same \"aquire/exploit\" strategy. FourPoint Energy is excited and proud of the technically advanced team of professionals who are hard-working, loyal, and committed to creating value for shareholders.'),
