	(6019,704,'timeline_items_10_timeline_description','In February, FourPoint announced the acquisition of all of the remaining Chesapeake Exploration, L.L.C. assets in the Western Anadarko Basin for $385 million. These assets included interest in XXX wells producing a combined XXX mmcfed and XXX net acres with a significant inventory of underdeveloped locations. To finance this acquisition, FourPoint issued a preferred equity of $600 million and expanded its borrowing base with its commercial bank group.'),
