	(7185,791,'timeline_items_5_timeline_description','CEP III held assets and operations in the Texas Panhandle, Western Oklahoma, and the East Texas Basin. During this period, the Cordillera management team executed on both small and large producing property and acreage acquisitions totaling over $700 million and has drilled over 235 wells (vertical and horizontal) investing over $300 million.'),
