	(7337,793,'timeline_items_7_timeline_description','In October of 2013, the core leadership from Cordillera formed a new venture under the name of FourPoint Energy. This fourth enterprise is the first company funded by direct equity investments and term debt rather than from a private equity fund. The initial geographic focus is the Western Anadarko and Permian Basins.'),
