	(218,2,'2016-03-30 22:26:10','2016-03-30 22:26:10','&nbsp;\r\n\r\nAt FourPoint our industry is energy but our business is opportunity. <a href=\"https://careers-fourpointenergy.icims.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more</a> about how your opportunities can grow alongside ours.\r\n\r\nFourPoint Energy is a leading independent, privately-owned exploration and production company headquartered in Denver, Colorado. FourPoint also operates four field offices located in Elk City and Woodward, Oklahoma, and Borger and Shamrock, Texas. Our entire team is committed to creating value that makes a difference by living out the <a href=\"http://fourpointenergy.com/about/who-we-are/\">values</a> that define FourPoint as an organization.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://careers-fourpointenergy.icims.com/\" target=\"_blank\">View open positions and apply</a>','Join Our Team','','publish','closed','closed','','join-our-team','','','2016-06-15 21:21:00','2016-06-15 21:21:00','',181,'http://fourpointenergy.com/?page_id=218',0,'page','',0),
