	(224,2,'2016-03-30 22:27:38','2016-03-30 22:27:38','&nbsp;\r\n\r\nFourPoint Energy is committed to ensuring all team members are able to enjoy a well-balanced benefit and compensation program.\r\n\r\nThe Human Resources team at FourPoint participates in and studies compensation surveys annually to ensure packages match or exceed industry standards. Setting, working toward and achieving goals are of utmost importance at FourPoint. This goal-oriented approach allows team members who make meaningful contributions to share in the success that FourPoint experiences. These goals and objectives are evaluated annually through FourPoint’s Performance Review and Incentive Compensation program.\r\n\r\nIn addition to a competitive compensation and bonus program, FourPoint Energy is proud to offer its employees a comprehensive benefit program, including:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Medical Insurance</li>\r\n 	<li>Dental Insurance</li>\r\n 	<li>Vision Insurance</li>\r\n 	<li>Life, Short-Term and Long-Term Disability Insurance</li>\r\n 	<li>Additional Voluntary Life Insurance</li>\r\n 	<li>Flexible Spending Account</li>\r\n 	<li>Paid Vacation, Sick Leave and Holidays</li>\r\n 	<li>401k with Employer Match</li>\r\n 	<li>Annual Bonus Potential</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nAdditional information regarding benefits and compensation will be provided to candidates going through FourPoint’s interview process.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://careers-fourpointenergy.icims.com/jobs/intro?hashed=-435679222\" target=\"_blank\">Apply to join the FourPoint team</a>','Benefits & Compensation','','publish','closed','closed','','benefits-compensation','','','2016-06-15 21:22:18','2016-06-15 21:22:18','',181,'http://fourpointenergy.com/?page_id=224',0,'page','',0),
