	(362,3,'2016-04-06 19:40:30','2016-04-06 19:40:30','While success in business and being the best is always at the forefront of the FourPoint organization, giving back provides the balance the team needs to remain focused. FourPoint Energy values Compassionate Stewardship by striving to positively impact the lives of employees, partners, landowners, and shareholders by caring for and about people, communities, assets and performance.\r\n\r\nThe team at FourPoint takes pride in being able to give back and make a difference in peoples’ lives, not only within the communities where employees live and work, but also on a national and global level. FourPoint values being a strong corporate citizen and encourages employees to enhance their quality of life by helping others both corporately and individually. FourPoint demonstrates support and community involvement in a variety of ways, from sponsored golf tournaments, luncheons, charitable donations, adopt-a-family programs, and numerous sponsored events within their operating communities.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-343\" src=\"http://fourpointenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/fpo800x450.png\" alt=\"fpo800x450\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" />\r\n\r\nFourPoint Energy believes in taking an active role for supporting local initiatives. The company is an active member of the:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>The Quarterly Forum</li>\r\n	<li>Kynd Hub</li>\r\n	<li>Canadian Chamber of Commerce</li>\r\n	<li>Wheeler Chamber of Commerce</li>\r\n	<li>Cheyenne - Roger Mills Chamber of Commerce</li>\r\n	<li>Canadian Rodeo</li>\r\n	<li>Arnett Rodeo</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n“We appreciate being part of the business community in the Texas Panhandle and Western Oklahoma. Our sponsorship and volunteer support of community groups and events is a small way to show our support for the communities where we live and work” – George Solich, President &amp; CEO','Community Engagement','','inherit','closed','closed','','215-revision-v1','','','2016-04-06 19:40:30','2016-04-06 19:40:30','',215,'http://fourpointenergy.com/2016/04/06/215-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(363,3,'2016-04-06 19:45:07','2016-04-06 19:45:07','Building on the experience of three very successful Cordillera companies over the last 15 years, you can expect our team at FourPoint to be deliberate and driven. We approach every day by making good decision with a sense of urgency. Although our name has changed, FourPoint Energy possesses the same passion for creating value for our shareholders, the same commitment to working “Better, Smarter, Faster”, and the same dedication to community stewardship.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-343\" src=\"http://fourpointenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/fpo800x450.png\" alt=\"fpo800x450\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" />\r\n\r\nFourPoint Energy promotes an opportunistic, performance-driven, and goal-oriented culture. Starting at the top with our executive management team moving across all functional areas we have a strong team-oriented approach to developing strategy, making decisions, and executing our plan. Since the company’s inception we have been blessed with dedicated employees, top-quality equity and debt partners, and high-quality assets to pursue investment of acquisition and drilling dollars. Our company culture focuses on creating value for shareholders with a hard-working, loyal, and technically advanced team of professionals.\r\n\r\nFourPoint Energy is proud to partner with landowners, mineral owners, drilling companies, service companies, suppliers, gatherers, transporters, consultants, and all our constituents in the responsible development of natural resources. We value our alliance and partnership with these constituents and approach each relationship with respect and integrity. The goal is to be the buyer of choice, lessee of choice, driller of choice, investment of choice, employer of choice, and eventually, seller of choice. We consider ourselves “Energy Farmers” and respect the land and its opportunity for multiple uses.\r\n\r\n<strong data-redactor-tag=\"strong\">Our Values:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Shared Vision – Creating an organization of people who share a long-term perspective driven to create value and enhance their quality of life.</li>\r\n	<li>Committed Teamwork – Fostering a respectful and inclusive environment to collaborate across functions, embracing the talents of individuals and trusting one another to make the best decisions.</li>\r\n	<li>Empowering People – Entrusting our people with responsibility and authority while making them accountable to our mission, values, and goals.</li>\r\n	<li>Driven to Excellence – Committing to deliberate and continuous improvement and striving to be the best with passion, integrity and humility.</li>\r\n	<li>Entrepreneurial – capturing valuable opportunities through adaptability, innovative thinking and strategic relationships.</li>\r\n	<li>Compassionate Stewardship – positively impacting the lives of our employees, partners, landowners and shareholders by caring for and about people, communities, assets and performance.</li>\r\n</ul>','Company Culture','','inherit','closed','closed','','221-revision-v1','','','2016-04-06 19:45:07','2016-04-06 19:45:07','',221,'http://fourpointenergy.com/2016/04/06/221-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(364,3,'2016-04-06 22:28:52','2016-04-06 22:28:52','<h3>Focus</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-356\" src=\"http://fourpointenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/fpo300x300.png\" alt=\"fpo300x300\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" />\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Core areas with concentrated assets</li>\r\n	<li>Opportunities for organic growth and acquisition growth</li>\r\n	<li>Long life gas reserves in active plays and basins</li>\r\n	<li>High margin, repeatable plays driven by good geology, engineering, high margins, and strong upside</li>\r\n	<li>Growth in production, cash flow, and reserves</li>\r\n	<li>Focus Areas: Western Anadarko and Permian Basins</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>People and Culture</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Practicing and living out company values and behaviors (hyperlink to values)</li>\r\n	<li>A results driven culture of opportunistic, performance-driven, and goal-oriented employees/partners</li>\r\n	<li>Experts in core areas by fine tuning the geologic/engineering model</li>\r\n	<li>Creative and adaptive to an always changing environment</li>\r\n	<li>Deliberate and selective - Building a team of “A” players</li>\r\n	<li>Develop a strong plan’ execute on the plan; stay focused and do it again and again</li>\r\n	<li>Dedicated to value creation with a sense of urgency</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Organic Oriented Growth</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-356\" src=\"http://fourpointenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/fpo300x300.png\" alt=\"fpo300x300\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" />\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Become the lessee of choice in each core area by doing what we said we’d do – be good stewards of the land and create value for our shareholders, landowners, royalty owners and communities in which we work</li>\r\n	<li>Build concentrated areas of leasehold to pursue a multi-rig drilling program to maximize efficiency and lessen delays in production and reserve growth</li>\r\n	<li>Emphasize geographic areas with quality production and reserve targets</li>\r\n	<li>Strive for win-win negotiations with landowners and surface owners to maximize the benefit to each party while mitigating the impact of our operations on the environment</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h3>Acquire &amp; Exploit Oriented Growth</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-356\" src=\"http://fourpointenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/fpo300x300.png\" alt=\"fpo300x300\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" />\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Aggressively pursue the purchase of producing properties in our core areas when we can capture additional upside opportunities, acquire additional leasehold, lower costs, and increase production and cash flow</li>\r\n	<li>Develop and build relationships, deliver results, make more deals</li>\r\n	<li>Pursue unsolicited and pre-emptive offers on assets that we can be an aggressive buyer</li>\r\n	<li>Evaluate and pursue only those competitive transactions where we have a distinctive competence which will make us the most competitive buyer</li>\r\n	<li>Be efficient and effective at multiple evaluations</li>\r\n	<li>Stay in the market at all times as a buyer and seller</li>\r\n	<li>Achieve critical mass in each core area through consistent growth in reserves, production, and cash flow</li>\r\n	<li>Aggressively exploit upside opportunities</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Financial Flexibility</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-356\" src=\"http://fourpointenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/fpo300x300.png\" alt=\"fpo300x300\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" />\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Seek strong, flexible, patient and market-savvy equity partners</li>\r\n	<li>Preserve enough capital to weather dramatic changes in commodity prices</li>\r\n	<li>Maintain a strong relationship with commercial banks to utilize debt as a meaningful, but fiscally prudent, part of the capital structure</li>\r\n	<li>Seek hedging opportunities that help to secure expenditures on drilling and underpin acquisition economics</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h3>The Franchise Concept</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-356\" src=\"http://fourpointenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/fpo300x300.png\" alt=\"fpo300x300\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" />\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Build great asset bases with strong production, cash flow, and upside opportunities</li>\r\n	<li>Gain critical mass within 48 to 60 months and pursue the sale of assets to growth oriented, quality focused exploration and production enterprises</li>\r\n	<li>Grow the next enterprise in the same geographic region with the same technical expertise</li>\r\n	<li>Become the top consolidator of a large resource base characterized by, focused, geographically concentrated, technically delineated, high-quality assets with strong production and cash flow, and enormous growth of potential of undeveloped reserves.</li>\r\n</ul>','Business Strategy','','inherit','closed','closed','','78-revision-v1','','','2016-04-06 22:28:52','2016-04-06 22:28:52','',78,'http://fourpointenergy.com/2016/04/06/78-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
