	(374,3,'2016-04-14 19:53:36','2016-04-14 19:53:36','<img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-342\" src=\"http://fourpointenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/fpo450x450.png\" alt=\"fpo450x450\" width=\"450\" height=\"450\" />\n\nFourPoint is primarily focused on acquiring and developing oil and natural gas assets in the Western Anadarko and Permian Basins. Founded by the leadership team of Cordillera Energy Partners following the sale to Apache Corporation in 2012, FourPoint Energy is proud to boast an exceptional team of professionals with over 30 years of industry-leading experience.\n\nFourPoint is committed to our mission of <strong data-redactor-tag=\"strong\"><em data-redactor-tag=\"em\">creating value that makes a difference</em></strong>. We strive to do this every day and in every part of the organization by fostering relationships with our investors, partners, land and mineral owners, vendors and employees with the highest level of respect and integrity. We are focused on continuous improvement through collaboration and innovation but also emphasize processes to maximize efficiencies.\n\nFourPoint is very proud of the culture and environment it has developed over the years. We are a dedicated team of individuals committed to carrying out our mission through six core values:\n<h3><strong data-redactor-tag=\"strong\">SHARED VISION</strong></h3>\nCreating an organization of people who share a long-term perspective driven to create value and enhance their quality of life.\n<h3><strong data-redactor-tag=\"strong\">COMMITTED TEAMWORK</strong></h3>\nFostering a respectful and inclusive environment to collaborate across functions, embracing the talents of individuals and trusting one another to make the best decisions.\n<h3><strong data-redactor-tag=\"strong\">EMPOWERING PEOPLE</strong></h3>\nEntrusting our people with responsibility and authority while making them accountable to our mission, values, and goals.\n<h3><strong data-redactor-tag=\"strong\">DRIVEN TO EXCELLENCE</strong></h3>\nCommitting to deliberate and continuous improvement and striving to be the best with passion, integrity and humility.\n<h3><strong data-redactor-tag=\"strong\">ENTREPRENEURIAL</strong></h3>\nCapturing valuable opportunities through adaptability, innovative thinking and strategic relationships.\n<h3><strong data-redactor-tag=\"strong\">COMPASSIONATE STEWARDSHIP</strong></h3>\nPositively impacting the lives of our employees, partners, landowners, and shareholders by caring for and about people, communities, assets and performance.','Who We Are','','inherit','closed','closed','','67-autosave-v1','','','2016-04-14 19:53:36','2016-04-14 19:53:36','',67,'http://fourpointenergy.com/2016/04/14/67-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(375,3,'2016-04-14 19:53:53','2016-04-14 19:53:53','<img class=\"size-full wp-image-342 alignright\" src=\"http://fourpointenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/fpo450x450.png\" alt=\"fpo450x450\" width=\"450\" height=\"450\" />\r\n\r\nFourPoint is primarily focused on acquiring and developing oil and natural gas assets in the Western Anadarko and Permian Basins. Founded by the leadership team of Cordillera Energy Partners following the sale to Apache Corporation in 2012, FourPoint Energy is proud to boast an exceptional team of professionals with over 30 years of industry-leading experience.\r\n\r\nFourPoint is committed to our mission of <strong data-redactor-tag=\"strong\"><em data-redactor-tag=\"em\">creating value that makes a difference</em></strong>. We strive to do this every day and in every part of the organization by fostering relationships with our investors, partners, land and mineral owners, vendors and employees with the highest level of respect and integrity. We are focused on continuous improvement through collaboration and innovation but also emphasize processes to maximize efficiencies.\r\n\r\nFourPoint is very proud of the culture and environment it has developed over the years. We are a dedicated team of individuals committed to carrying out our mission through six core values:\r\n<h3><strong data-redactor-tag=\"strong\">SHARED VISION</strong></h3>\r\nCreating an organization of people who share a long-term perspective driven to create value and enhance their quality of life.\r\n<h3><strong data-redactor-tag=\"strong\">COMMITTED TEAMWORK</strong></h3>\r\nFostering a respectful and inclusive environment to collaborate across functions, embracing the talents of individuals and trusting one another to make the best decisions.\r\n<h3><strong data-redactor-tag=\"strong\">EMPOWERING PEOPLE</strong></h3>\r\nEntrusting our people with responsibility and authority while making them accountable to our mission, values, and goals.\r\n<h3><strong data-redactor-tag=\"strong\">DRIVEN TO EXCELLENCE</strong></h3>\r\nCommitting to deliberate and continuous improvement and striving to be the best with passion, integrity and humility.\r\n<h3><strong data-redactor-tag=\"strong\">ENTREPRENEURIAL</strong></h3>\r\nCapturing valuable opportunities through adaptability, innovative thinking and strategic relationships.\r\n<h3><strong data-redactor-tag=\"strong\">COMPASSIONATE STEWARDSHIP</strong></h3>\r\nPositively impacting the lives of our employees, partners, landowners, and shareholders by caring for and about people, communities, assets and performance.','Who We Are','','inherit','closed','closed','','67-revision-v1','','','2016-04-14 19:53:53','2016-04-14 19:53:53','',67,'http://fourpointenergy.com/2016/04/14/67-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(376,3,'2016-04-14 19:55:22','2016-04-14 19:55:22','<img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-342\" src=\"http://fourpointenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/fpo450x450.png\" alt=\"fpo450x450\" width=\"450\" height=\"450\" />\r\n<h3>Why lease or sell to FourPoint Energy?</h3>\r\n<h4>Aggressive Offers</h4>\r\nWe pay at or above market based terms and are experienced to move quickly on simple or complex trades.\r\n<h4>Defined Areas of Focus:</h4>\r\nOur leasing is focused on areas where FourPoint actively drills and operates.\r\n<h4>Active Developer</h4>\r\nWe are not an asset warehouse. Our business strategy employs an acquisition development model that accelerates the pace of value creation.\r\n<h4>Financial Strength</h4>\r\nAs a privately funded company, we have a strong balance sheet with over $2.5 billion of committed capital and backing from some of the largest funds in private equity.\r\n<h4>Highly Experienced Team:</h4>\r\nOur team of engineers, geologists, landman and other professionals have a strong experience base. We are committed to capturing valuable opportunities through adaptability, innovative thinking, and strategic relationships. This translates to being able to execute on leasing, drilling and acquisitions in the most efficient and effective manner.\r\n<h4>Experienced Vertical and Horizontal Driller:</h4>\r\nWe have a dedicated team of drilling and completion engineers as well as development geologists that have drilled and completed over 320 operated wells in the last 16 years with nearly 200 of those in the modern horizontal environment.\r\n<h4>Active Producing Property Buyer:</h4>\r\nWith over 30 years of demonstrated acquisition experience to evaluate and pay for producing and undeveloped reserves, FourPoint has closed over ___ acquisition transactions ranging in size from less than $1 million to $1 Billion.\r\n<h4>Responsible Operator:</h4>\r\nWe are a prudent, responsible, low cost operator. We have a disciplined approach to efficiency and cost reduction. Our technical team is highly experienced in drilling and completions in both horizontal and vertical wells. We are committed to the safe and environmentally responsible development of our energy resources and invest time and resources to improve the communities in which we live and work.\r\n<h4>Relationship Driven:</h4>\r\nOur acquisition strategy incorporates a win-win philosophy to deal making. We strive to build long-term relationships and partnerships that stimulate additional transactions down the road.\r\n<h4>Farmouts and Joint-Ventures:</h4>\r\nWe encourage owners to provide us the opportunity to accelerate the development of their acreage via farmout or joint-venture agreements.\r\n<div class=\"opp-contact\">\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Contact for Leasing:</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Scott Haselwood</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Senior Land Advisor, Manager of Leasing\r\n(303) 785-1547 (direct)\r\n(303) 290-9997 (fax)\r\n(303) 720-877-1564 (cell)\r\nEmail: <a href=\"mailto:shaselwood@fourpointenergy.com\"><u data-redactor-tag=\"u\">shaselwood@fourpointenergy.com</u></a></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"opp-contact\">\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Contact for Asset Sales:</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Brad Marvin</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Vice President, Business Development\r\n(303) 785-1554 (direct)\r\n(303) 290-9997 (fax)\r\n(303) 974-0275 (cell)\r\nEmail: <a href=\"mailto:bmarvin@fourpointenergy.com\"><u data-redactor-tag=\"u\">bmarvin@fourpointenergy.com</u></a></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>Main areas of focus for leasing and asset acquisitions</h3>\r\n<h4>Active Plays</h4>\r\nWestern Anadarko Basin: Texas Panhandle &amp; Western Oklahoma\r\n<h4>Areas of Focus</h4>\r\n<strong>New Mexico:</strong>\r\n\r\nLea, Eddy\r\n\r\n<strong>Texas:</strong>\r\n\r\nLoving, Culberson, Winkler, Ward, Reeves, Martin, Howard, Glasscock, Midland, Upton, Reagan\r\nOperating Counties\r\n\r\n<stron