	(455,2,'2016-04-18 20:52:55','2016-04-18 20:52:55','FourPoint Energy values the power of relationships, specifically those with our surface and mineral interest owners. Our goal is to be the lessee of choice in each of our core areas by building positive impactful relationships, being good stewards of the land, and known and respected for our integrity as an operator.  To better serve our owners, FourPoint Energy offers easy ways for owners to access copies of revenue checks and joint interest billings electronically. Additionally, we have provided easy instructions on how to read both your revenue check stub and your joint interest billing statements. We have also provided information on ownership changes and answers to frequently asked questions.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>For owner relation inquiries please call 303.785.1581 or email <a href=\"mailto:ownerrelations@fourpointenergy.com\"><u data-redactor-tag=\"u\">ownerrelations@fourpointenergy.com</u></a></li>\r\n	<li>For Division Order Inquiries please email <a href=\"mailto:divisionorders@fourpointnergy.com\"><u data-redactor-tag=\"u\">divisionorders@fourpointnergy.com</u></a></li>\r\n	<li>Interested in Direct Deposit? &lt;Form&gt;</li>\r\n	<li>To access copies of revenue checks please<a href=\"https://secure.pds-austin.com/fourpoint/login.asp\" target=\"_blank\"> <u data-redactor-tag=\"u\">click here</u></a></li>\r\n</ul>','Owner Information','','inherit','closed','closed','','187-revision-v1','','','2016-04-18 20:52:55','2016-04-18 20:52:55','',187,'http://fourpointenergy.com/2016/04/18/187-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
