	(569,2,'2016-04-22 02:10:30','2016-04-22 02:10:30','FourPoint Energy values the power of relationships, specifically those with our surface and mineral interest owners. To better serve our owners, FourPoint Energy offers easy ways for owners to access copies of revenue checks and joint interest billings electronically.\r\n\r\nAdditionally, we have provided easy instructions on how to read both your revenue check stub and your joint interest billing statements. We have also provided information on ownership changes and answers to frequently asked questions.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>For owner relation inquiries please call 303.785.1581 or email <a href=\"mailto:ownerrelations@fourpointenergy.com\">ownerrelations@fourpointenergy.com</a></li>\r\n	<li>For Division Order Inquiries please email <a href=\"mailto:divisionorders@fourpointnergy.com\">divisionorders@fourpointnergy.com</a></li>\r\n	<li>Interested in Direct Deposit? &lt;Form&gt;</li>\r\n	<li>To access copies of revenue checks please<a href=\"https://secure.pds-austin.com/fourpoint/login.asp\" target=\"_blank\"> <u data-redactor-tag=\"u\">click here</u></a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;','Owner Information','','inherit','closed','closed','','187-revision-v1','','','2016-04-22 02:10:30','2016-04-22 02:10:30','',187,'http://fourpointenergy.com/2016/04/22/187-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(570,2,'2016-04-22 02:19:44','2016-04-22 02:19:44','While success in business and being the best is always at the forefront of the FourPoint organization, giving back provides the balance our organization values as part of the team. FourPoint Energy values Compassionate Stewardship by striving to positively impact the lives of employees, partners, landowners, and shareholders by caring for and about people, communities, assets and performance.\r\n\r\nThe team at FourPoint takes pride in being able to give back and make a difference in peoples’ lives, not only within the communities where employees live and work, but also on a national and global level. FourPoint values being a strong corporate citizen and encourages employees to enhance their quality of life by helping others both corporately and individually. FourPoint demonstrates support and community involvement in a variety of ways, from sponsored charity events, luncheons, charitable donations, adopt-a-family programs, holiday charitable donations and numerous sponsored events within their operating communities.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-343\" src=\"http://fourpointenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/fpo800x450.png\" alt=\"fpo800x450\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" />\r\n\r\nFourPoint Energy believes in taking an active role for supporting local initiatives. The company is an active member of the:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>The Quarterly Forum</li>\r\n	<li>Kynd Hub</li>\r\n	<li>Canadian Chamber of Commerce</li>\r\n	<li>Wheeler Chamber of Commerce</li>\r\n	<li>Cheyenne - Roger Mills Chamber of Commerce</li>\r\n	<li>Elk City Chamber of Commerce</li>\r\n	<li>Canadian Rodeo</li>\r\n	<li>Arnett Rodeo</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<em>“We appreciate being part of the business community in the Texas Panhandle and Western Oklahoma. Our sponsorship and volunteer support of community groups and events is a small way to show our support for the communities where we live and work”</em> – George Solich, President &amp; CEO','Community Engagement','','inherit','closed','closed','','215-revision-v1','','','2016-04-22 02:19:44','2016-04-22 02:19:44','',215,'http://fourpointenergy.com/2016/04/22/215-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
