	(593,2,'2016-04-25 19:23:19','2016-04-25 19:23:19','Revenue checks are mailed monthly by the last day of the second month following the month of production. Revenue checks are mailed to all owners with a balance due to them of over $100.00. If the balance on your account is not over $100.00, a revenue check may not be issued to you each month. Once a year, typically in the spring, revenue checks will be mailed to all owners with a balance due to them of over $10.00.','Why have I not received a revenue check?','','publish','closed','closed','','not-received-revenue-check','','','2016-04-25 19:23:19','2016-04-25 19:23:19','',0,'http://fourpointenergy.com/?post_type=faq&#038;p=593',6,'faq','',0),
