	(632,1,'2016-04-29 06:12:49','2016-04-29 06:12:49','<img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-356\" src=\"http://fourpointenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/fpo300x300.png\" alt=\"fpo300x300\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" />\r\n<h3>FourPoint Energy, LLC</h3>\r\n100 St. Paul Street, Suite 400\r\nDenver, CO 80206\r\n\r\n(303) 290-0990 Main\r\n(303) 290-9997 Fax\r\n<h3>All Owner Inquiries</h3>\r\n<strong data-redactor-tag=\"strong\">Phone:</strong> (303) 785-1581\r\n\r\nYou will be prompted to leave a message when contacting our owner inquiry line. Please leave your:\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Name</li>\r\n 	<li>Telephone Number</li>\r\n 	<li>Owner Number</li>\r\n 	<li>A brief description of your inquiry</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nYour owner number is the five digit number located in the bottom left corner of your check stub, or the top right hand corner of your joint owner statement.\r\n\r\nEvery effort will be made to make an initial response to your inquiry within 24 hours. Please do not leave more than one message as this will delay our response time.\r\n\r\n<strong data-redactor-tag=\"strong\">Email:</strong>\r\n\r\nAccounting Inquiries: <a href=\"mailto:ownerrelations@fourpointenergy.com\"><u data-redactor-tag=\"u\">ownerrelations@fourpointenergy.com</u></a>\r\n\r\nDivision Owner Inquiries: <a href=\"mailto:divisionorders@fourpointenergy.com\"><u data-redactor-tag=\"u\"> divisionorders@fourpointenergy.com</u></a>','Contact Information','','inherit','closed','closed','','200-revision-v1','','','2016-04-29 06:12:49','2016-04-29 06:12:49','',200,'http://fourpointenergy.com/2016/04/29/200-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
