	(647,1,'2016-04-29 06:43:29','2016-04-29 06:43:29','To help assist you with your request to make a change to your ownership account, we have provided a list of situations and occurrences that require changes be made to your account. The list provides the documentation FourPoint Energy will need in order to complete the change to your ownership account. All change requests must be submitted in writing.\r\n\r\nShould you have any additional questions regarding the documentation required to complete a change to your account, please feel free to contact us at (303) 785-1581 or <a href=\"mailto:ownerrelations@fourpointenergy.com\"><u data-redactor-tag=\"u\">ownerrelations@fourpointenergy.com</u></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://fourpointenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/Change-of-ownership_2.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Click here</a> to download Change Of Ownership guide.','Change of Ownership','','inherit','closed','closed','','197-revision-v1','','','2016-04-29 06:43:29','2016-04-29 06:43:29','',197,'http://fourpointenergy.com/2016/04/29/197-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(648,1,'2016-04-29 06:43:44','2016-04-29 06:43:44','<img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-356\" src=\"http://fourpointenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/fpo300x300.png\" alt=\"fpo300x300\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" />\r\n<h3>FourPoint Energy, LLC</h3>\r\n100 St. Paul Street, Suite 400\r\nDenver, CO 80206\r\n\r\n(303) 290-0990 Main\r\n(303) 290-9997 Fax\r\n<h3>All Owner Inquiries</h3>\r\n<strong data-redactor-tag=\"strong\">Phone:</strong> (303) 785-1581\r\n\r\nYou will be prompted to leave a message when contacting our owner inquiry line. Please leave your:\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Name</li>\r\n 	<li>Telephone Number</li>\r\n 	<li>Owner Number</li>\r\n 	<li>A brief description of your inquiry</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nYour owner number is the five digit number located in the bottom left corner of your check stub, or the top right hand corner of your joint owner statement.\r\n\r\nEvery effort will be made to make an initial response to your inquiry within 24 hours. Please do not leave more than one message as this will delay our response time.\r\n\r\n<strong data-redactor-tag=\"strong\">Email:</strong>\r\n\r\nAccounting Inquiries: <a href=\"mailto:ownerrelations@fourpointenergy.com\"><u data-redactor-tag=\"u\">ownerrelations@fourpointenergy.com</u></a>\r\n\r\nDivision Owner Inquiries: <a href=\"mailto:divisionorders@fourpointenergy.com\"><u data-redactor-tag=\"u\"> divisionorders@fourpointenergy.com</u></a>','Contact Information','','inherit','closed','closed','','200-revision-v1','','','2016-04-29 06:43:44','2016-04-29 06:43:44','',200,'http://fourpointenergy.com/2016/04/29/200-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
