	(743,2,'2016-06-09 19:24:01','2016-06-09 19:24:01','At FourPoint our industry is energy but our business is opportunity. <a href=\"https://careers-fourpointenergy.icims.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more about</a> how your opportunities can grow alongside ours.\n\nFourPoint Energy is a leading independent privately owned exploration and production company. Based in Denver, Colorado, FourPoint also has field offices in Woodward, Oklahoma, Borger, Texas, Elk City, Oklahoma, and Shamrock, Texas. FourPoint is committed to creating value that makes a difference by living out the values that define FourPoint as an organization.\n\n<a href=\"https://careers-fourpointenergy.icims.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Join our team and apply </a>\n\n&nbsp;\n\nAt FourPoint our industry is energy but our business is opportunity. Learn more about how your opportunities can grow alongside ours.\n\nFourPoint Energy is a leading independent, privately-owned exploration and production company headquartered in Denver, Colorado. FourPoint also operates four field offices located in Elk City and Woodward, Oklahoma, and Borger and Shamrock, Texas. Our entire team is committed to creating value that makes a difference by living out the values (hyperlink) that define FourPoint as an organization.\n\n<a href=\"https://careers-fourpointenergy.icims.com/\" target=\"_blank\">View open positions and apply</a>','Join Our Team','','inherit','closed','closed','','218-autosave-v1','','','2016-06-09 19:24:01','2016-06-09 19:24:01','',218,'http://fourpointenergy.com/2016/05/05/218-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(744,2,'2016-05-05 19:38:11','2016-05-05 19:38:11','At FourPoint, our industry is energy but our business is opportunity. <a href=\"https://careers-fourpointenergy.icims.com/\">Apply and view</a> our current openings to see how your opportunities can grow alongside ours.\r\n\r\nFourPoint Energy is a leading independent privately owned exploration and production company based in Denver, Colorado with field offices in Woodward and Elk City, Oklahoma and Borger and Shamrock, Texas. We are committed to creating value that makes a difference by practicing and living out our values (hyperlink) that define us as an organization.','Join Our Team','','inherit','closed','closed','','218-revision-v1','','','2016-05-05 19:38:11','2016-05-05 19:38:11','',218,'http://fourpointenergy.com/2016/05/05/218-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(745,2,'2016-06-13 22:26:52','2016-06-13 22:26:52','&nbsp;\n\nBuilding on the experience of three very successful Cordillera companies, you can expect the team at FourPoint to be deliberate and driven. We approach every day by making good decisions with a sense of urgency.\n\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1102\" src=\"http://fourpointenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/companyculture.jpg\" alt=\"companyculture\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1000\" />\n\nFourPoint promotes an opportunistic, performance-driven, and goal-oriented culture. Starting at the top with our executive management team, moving across all functional areas, we have a strong team-oriented approach to developing strategy, making decisions, and achieving our goals. Since the company’s inception we have been blessed with dedicated employees, top-tier equity and debt partners, and high-quality assets to pursue investment of acquisition and drilling dollars. Our company culture focuses on creating value for shareholders with a hard-working, loyal, and technically advanced team of professionals.\n\nFourPoint is proud to partner with landowners, mineral owners, drilling companies, service companies, suppliers, gatherers, transporters, consultants, and all our constituents in the responsible development of natural resources. We value our alliance with these constituents and approach each relationship with respect and integrity. We consider it an honor to find and produce energy for America and have the utmost respect for the land and the opportunities it provides.\n<h2></h2>\n<h2>FourPoint carries out our mission through six core values:</h2>\n<h3><strong>Shared Vision</strong></h3>\nCreating an organization of people who share a long-term perspective driven to create value and enhance their quality of life.\n<h3><strong>Committed Teamwork</strong></h3>\nFostering a respectful and inclusive environment to collaborate across functions, embracing the talents of individuals and trusting one another to make the best decisions.\n<h3><strong>Empowering People</strong></h3>\nEntrusting our people with responsibility and authority while making them accountable to our mission, values, and goals.\n<h3><strong>Driven to Excellence</strong></h3>\nCommitting to deliberate and continuous improvement and striving to be the best with passion, integrity and humility.\n<h3><strong>Entrepreneurial</strong></h3>\nCapturing valuable opportunities through adaptability, innovative thinking and strategic relationships.\n<h3><strong>Compassionate Stewardship</strong></h3>\nPositively impacting the lives of our employees, partners, landowners and shareholders by caring for and about people, communities, assets and performance.','Our Culture','','inherit','closed','closed','','221-autosave-v1','','','2016-06-13 22:26:52','2016-06-13 22:26:52','',221,'http://fourpointenergy.com/2016/05/05/221-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(746,2,'2016-05-05 19:43:39','2016-05-05 19:43:39','Building on the experience of three very successful Cordillera companies over the last 15 years, you can expect our team at FourPoint to be deliberate and driven. We approach every day by making good decision with a sense of urgency.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-343\" src=\"http://fourpointenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/fpo800x450.png\" alt=\"fpo800x450\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" />\r\n\r\nFourPoint Energy promotes an opportunistic, performance-driven, and goal-oriented culture. Starting at the top with our executive management team moving across all functional areas we have a strong team-oriented approach to developing strategy, making decisions, and executing our plan. Since the company’s inception we have been blessed with dedicated employees, top-quality equity and debt partners, and high-quality assets to pursue investment of acquisition and drilling dollars. Our company culture focuses on creating value for shareholders with a hard-working, loyal, and technically advanced team of professionals.\r\n\r\nFourPoint Energy is proud to partner with landowners, mineral owners, drilling companies, service companies, suppliers, gatherers, transporters, consultants, and all our constituents in the responsible development of natural resources. We value our alliance and partnership with these constituents and approach each relationship with respect and integrity. The goal is to be the buyer of choice, lessee of choice, driller of choice, investment of choice, employer of choice, and eventually, seller of choice. We consider ourselves “Energy Farmers” and respect the land and its opportunity for multiple uses.\r\n\r\n<strong data-redactor-tag=\"strong\">Our Values:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Driven to Excellence: Committing to deliberate and continuous improvement and striving to be the best with passion, integrity and humility.</li>\r\n 	<li>Entrepreneurial: Capturing valuable opportunities through adaptability, innovative thinking and strategic relationships.</li>\r\n 	<li>Empowering People: Entrusting our people with responsibility and authority while making them accountable to our mission, values, and goals.</li>\r\n 	<li>Committed Teamwork: Fostering a respectful and inclusive environment to collaborate across functions, embracing the talents of individuals and trusting one another to make the best decisions.</li>\r\n 	<li>Shared Vision: Creating an organization of people who share a long-term perspective driven to create value and enhance their quality of life.</li>\r\n 	<li>Compassionate Stewardship: Positively impacting the lives of our employees, partners, landowners, and shareholders by caring for and about people, communities, assets and performance.</li>\r\n</ul>','Company Culture','','inherit','closed','closed','','221-revision-v1','','','2016-05-05 19:43:39','2016-05-05 19:43:39','',221,'http://fourpointenergy.com/2016/05/05/221-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(747,2,'2016-05-05 20:05:57','2016-05-05 20:05:57','FourPoint provides hands-on training for interns, who may work in the following Departments:\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Accounting</li>\r\n 	<li>Land</li>\r\n 	<li>Geology</li>\r\n 	<li>Reservoir and Production Engineering</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nTo view all of our current intern program openings and to apply, please <a href=\"https://careers-fourpointenergy.icims.com\" target=\"_blank\">click here</a>.\r\n\r\nFourPoint summer interns have represented the following universities:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Arizona State University</li>\r\n 	<li>Colorado School of Mines</li>\r\n 	<li>Colorado State University</li>\r\n 	<li>Duke University</li>\r\n 	<li>Metropolitan State College of Denver</li>\r\n 	<li>University of Colorado</li>\r\n 	<li>University of Kansas</li>\r\n 	<li>University of Wyoming</li>\r\n 	<li>Western State University</li>\r\n 	<li>Princeton University</li>\r\n</ul>','Internship Program','','inherit','closed','closed','','227-revision-v1','','','2016-05-05 20:05:57','2016-05-05 20:05:57','',227,'http://fourpointenergy.com/2016/05/05/227-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
