	(749,2,'2016-05-05 20:10:57','2016-05-05 20:10:57','Your privacy and the privacy of all the users of the FourPoint web site (“FourPointEnergy.com”) are very important to FourPoint Energy. The following privacy statement tells you, among other things, what information FourPoint gathers from you on FourPointEnergy.com, how it may be used or disclosed by FourPoint, and the efforts FourPoint makes to protect it. Please read this statement carefully. If you have any questions, please contact FourPoint Energy at <a href=\"mailto:webmaster@fourpointenergy.com\">webmaster@fourpointenergy.com</a>\r\n\r\n<strong><u data-redactor-tag=\"u\">Information We Collect From You</u></strong>\r\n\r\nIn general, you can visit this Website without telling us who you are or revealing any information about yourself. Our web servers collect the domain names, not the email addresses, of visitors. Our web servers (as many Websites do) place a “cookie” (a small data file) on your computer’s hard drive, which allows the server to determine the computer when it visits again, in order to track statistical information about navigation to and throughout certain areas of our site. This cookie is not used to obtain your name or any personal data, and the information that is tracked is used only for internal purposes, such as to improve site navigation and to measure the effectiveness of our placements, and is not shared with anyone other than FourPoint affiliates and contractors who assist FourPoint in these efforts and are bound to confidentiality. However, if you prefer not to accept cookies, you can set your browser to reject them or to alert you before one is placed.\r\n\r\nIn addition, there are portions of this Website where we may need to collect personal information from you for a specific purpose, such as to provide you with certain information you request. The information collected from you may include your name, address, telephone, fax number or email address.\r\n\r\n<strong><u data-redactor-tag=\"u\">Our Use of Your Information</u></strong>\r\n\r\nFourPoint uses the information collected to provide you with a better website. Additionally, FourPoint may use certain pieces of personal information, collected through registration or otherwise, to construct aggregate demographic or statistical pictures of FourPointEnergy.com users and the transactions conducted using the system.','Privacy Statement','','inherit','closed','closed','','507-revision-v1','','','2016-05-05 20:10:57','2016-05-05 20:10:57','',507,'http://fourpointenergy.com/2016/05/05/507-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
