	(757,2,'2016-05-06 17:30:42','2016-05-06 17:30:42','<h4>How do I contact FourPoint Energy?</h4>\r\nA: Visit our \"Contact Us\" page\r\n\r\nQ: How do I make changes to my account?\r\n\r\nA: Visit our “Change of Ownership” section\r\n\r\nQ: Can I setup direct deposit of revenue checks?\r\n\r\nA: Download our direct deposit form. Please print the form, complete it in its entirety and return by mail along with a voided check to: 100 Saint Paul Street, Suite 400, Denver, CO 80206 or email us at: ownerrelations@fourpointenergy.com\r\n\r\nQ: I returned my direct deposit form. Why did I receive another check in the mail?\r\n\r\nA: Please allow 60 days for us to process your direct deposit request. If you mailed your form more than 60 days ago, please contact us at (303) 785-1581 or <a href=\"mailto:ownerrelations@fourpointenergy.com\">ownerrelations@fourpointenergy.com</a>.\r\n\r\nQ: Why have I not received a revenue check?\r\n\r\nA: Revenue checks are mailed monthly by the last day of the second month following the month of production. Revenue checks are mailed to all owners with a balance due to them of over $100.00. If the balance on your account is not over $100.00, a revenue check may not be issued to you each month. Once a year, typically in the spring, revenue checks will be mailed to all owners with a balance due to them of over $10.00.\r\n\r\nQ:Can I receive my revenue checks even if the account balance is under $100.00?\r\nA: Please submit a request in writing with the dollar amount you would like to have revenue checks mailed to you, to <a href=\"mailto:ownerinq@cordilleraep.com\">ownerrelations@fourpointenergy.com</a>.\r\n\r\nQ: When can I expect to receive my 1099?\r\nA: Your 1099 will be mailed to you no later than January 31st. Please allow 10 business days after January 31st before contacting us regarding not receiving your 1099.\r\n\r\nQ: What should I do if my check is lost or stolen?\r\nA: Please allow 10 business days after checks are mailed to receive your check. If after 10 business days you have still not received your revenue check please contact us at (303) 785-1581 or <a href=\"mailto:ownerinq@cordilleraep.com\">ownerrelations@fourpointenergy.com</a>. If your check is stolen please contact us at (303) 785-1581 or <a href=\"mailto:ownerinq@cordilleraep.com\">ownerrelations@fourpointenergy.com</a>.\r\n\r\nQ: How do I get a copy of my revenue check or joint interest billing?\r\nA: All revenue check detail is available at <a href=\"http://www.energylink.com/\">www.energylink.com</a>. Please contact us at (303) 785-1581 or <a href=\"mailto:ownerinq@cordilleraep.com\">ownerrelations@fourpointenergy.com</a> to receive your user ID and password for EnergyLink.\r\n\r\nQ: Why did you send me an IRS Form W-9?\r\n\r\nA: The IRS requires that we confirm your Tax ID number every year and keep the W-9 on file. Please complete the form using the name provided on your revenue check, and your Social Security number or Tax ID number.','FAQ','','inherit','closed','closed','','514-revision-v1','','','2016-05-06 17:30:42','2016-05-06 17:30:42','',514,'http://fourpointenergy.com/2016/05/06/514-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
