	(1143,2,'2016-06-13 20:59:13','2016-06-13 20:59:13','<h3><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1142\" src=\"http://fourpointenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/strategy.jpg\" alt=\"strategy\" width=\"1639\" height=\"931\" /></h3>\r\n<h3>People, Culture and Technology</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Dedicated to creating value guided by our company <a href=\"http://fourpointenergy.com/about/who-we-are/\">values</a> and behaviors</li>\r\n 	<li>Support and embody a results-driven culture of opportunistic, performance-driven, and goal-oriented employees and partners</li>\r\n 	<li>Focus and adapt to an always changing environment</li>\r\n 	<li>Be deliberate and selective in building a team of “A” players</li>\r\n 	<li>Develop competitive advantages in core areas driven by a thorough technical playbook, an active development plan and a transaction oriented culture</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Acquisitions, Divestitures and Joint Ventures</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Aggressively pursue the acquisition of quality assets where we can capture additional upside opportunities, acquire additional leasehold, lower costs and increase production and cash flow</li>\r\n 	<li>Evaluate and pursue only those transactions where we have a strong competitive advantage to further create value</li>\r\n 	<li>Strive for efficiency and effectiveness in multiple evaluations and transactions and be in the market at all times</li>\r\n 	<li>Position ourselves as the buyer of choice, the seller of choice and partner of choice</li>\r\n 	<li>Develop, build and maintain strong industry relationships.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Organic Growth and Operating Efficiency</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Organic growth through the drilling and development of our low-risk drilling inventory</li>\r\n 	<li>Maximize operational footprint to control quality and pace of development</li>\r\n 	<li>Consistent increase in production, cash flow, and reserves through drilling, leasing, and acquiring</li>\r\n 	<li>Maximize margins with efficient and safe operations</li>\r\n 	<li>Utilize the best technology and develop long-term relationships with service providers to achieve best-in-class capital efficiencies and results</li>\r\n 	<li>Maintain a culture of continuous improvement in operational efficiencies, integration of best drilling and completion technologies, and strong performance through safe and environmentally responsible procedures</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Financial Flexibility</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Seek strong, flexible, patient and market-savvy capital partners</li>\r\n 	<li>Maintain the appropriate amount of liquidity to weather the volatility in the commodity markets</li>\r\n 	<li>Structure equity and debt on the balance sheet to minimize cost and maximize utilization to build and develop assets with a sense of urgency</li>\r\n 	<li>Maintain strong relationships with both equity and debt providers allowing us to be entrepreneurial in capturing additional opportunities</li>\r\n 	<li>Pursue a consistent and measured hedging strategy to protect future cash flow and underpin acquisition economics</li>\r\n</ul>','Business Strategy','','inherit','closed','closed','','78-revision-v1','','','2016-06-13 20:59:13','2016-06-13 20:59:13','',78,'http://fourpointenergy.com/78-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(1144,2,'2016-06-13 21:02:04','2016-06-13 21:02:04','<h3><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1142\" src=\"http://fourpointenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/strategy.jpg\" alt=\"strategy\" width=\"1639\" height=\"931\" /></h3>\r\n<h3>People, Culture and Technology</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Dedicated to creating value guided by our company <a href=\"http://fourpointenergy.com/about/who-we-are/\">values</a> and behaviors</li>\r\n 	<li>Support and embody a results-driven culture of opportunistic, performance-driven, and goal-oriented employees and partners</li>\r\n 	<li>Focus and adapt to an always changing environment</li>\r\n 	<li>Be deliberate and selective in building a team of “A” players</li>\r\n 	<li>Develop competitive advantages in core areas driven by a thorough technical playbook, an active development plan and a transaction oriented culture</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Acquisitions, Divestitures and Joint Ventures</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Aggressively pursue the acquisition of quality assets where we can capture additional upside opportunities, acquire additional leasehold, lower costs and increase production and cash flow</li>\r\n 	<li>Evaluate and pursue only those transactions where we have a strong competitive advantage to further create value</li>\r\n 	<li>Strive for efficiency and effectiveness in multiple evaluations and transactions and be in the market at all times</li>\r\n 	<li>Position ourselves as the buyer of choice, the seller of choice and partner of choice</li>\r\n 	<li>Develop, build and maintain strong industry relationships.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Organic Growth and Operating Efficiency</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Organic growth through the development of our low-risk drilling inventory</li>\r\n 	<li>Maximize operational footprint to control quality and pace of development</li>\r\n 	<li>Consistent increase in production, cash flow, and reserves through drilling, leasing, and acquiring</li>\r\n 	<li>Maximize margins with efficient and safe operations</li>\r\n 	<li>Utilize the best technology and develop long-term relationships with service providers to achieve best-in-class capital efficiencies and results</li>\r\n 	<li>Maintain a culture of continuous improvement in operational efficiencies, integration of best drilling and completion technologies, and strong performance through safe and environmentally responsible procedures</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Financial Flexibility</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Seek strong, flexible, patient and market-savvy capital partners</li>\r\n 	<li>Maintain the appropriate amount of liquidity to weather the volatility in the commodity markets</li>\r\n 	<li>Structure equity and debt on the balance sheet to minimize cost and maximize flexibility to build and develop assets with a sense of urgency</li>\r\n 	<li>Maintain strong relationships with both equity and debt providers allowing us to be entrepreneurial in capturing additional opportunities</li>\r\n 	<li>Pursue a consistent and measured hedging strategy to protect future cash flow and underpin acquisition economics</li>\r\n</ul>','Business Strategy','','inherit','closed','closed','','78-revision-v1','','','2016-06-13 21:02:04','2016-06-13 21:02:04','',78,'http://fourpointenergy.com/78-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
