	(1155,2,'2016-06-13 21:14:59','2016-06-13 21:14:59','<h2>How do I contact FourPoint Energy?</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Visit our <a href=\"http://fourpointenergy.com/interest-owners/contact-information/\">\"Contact Us\"</a> page</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>How do I make changes to my account?</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Visit our <a href=\"http://fourpointenergy.com/interest-owners/change-of-ownership/\">“Change of Ownership”</a> section</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Can I setup direct deposit of revenue checks?</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Download our <a href=\"http://fourpointenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/FourPoint_DirectDepositEnrollment2016-with-mailing-info.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">direct deposit</a> form. Please print the form, complete it in its entirety and return by mail along with a voided check to:\r\n<strong>100 St. Paul Street, Ste. 400</strong>\r\n<strong> Denver, CO 80206</strong>\r\n<strong> email: </strong><a href=\"mailto:ownerrelations@fourpointenergy.com\">ownerrelations@fourpointenergy.com</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>I returned my direct deposit form. Why did I receive another check in the mail?</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Please allow 60 days for us to process your direct deposit request. If you mailed your form more than 60 days ago, please contact us at:\r\n<strong>(303) 785-1581</strong>\r\n<strong>email: </strong><a href=\"mailto:ownerrelations@fourpointenergy.com\">ownerrelations@fourpointenergy.com</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Why have I not received a revenue check?</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Revenue checks are mailed monthly by the last day of the second month following the month of production. Revenue checks are mailed to all owners with a balance due to them of over $100.00. If the balance on your account is not over $100.00, a revenue check may not be issued to you each month. Once a year, typically in the spring, revenue checks will be mailed to all owners with a balance due to them of over $10.00.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Can I receive my revenue checks even if the account balance is under $100.00?</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Please submit a request in writing with the dollar amount you would like to have revenue checks mailed to you. Please submit this request to <a href=\"mailto:ownerinq@cordilleraep.com\">ownerrelations@fourpointenergy.com</a>.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>When can I expect to receive my 1099?</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Your 1099 will be mailed to you no later than January 31st. Please allow 10 business days after January 31st before contacting us regarding not receiving your 1099.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>What should I do if my check is lost or stolen?</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Please allow 10 business days after checks are mailed to receive your check. If after 10 business days you have still not received your revenue check please contact us at:\r\n<strong>(303) 785-1581</strong>\r\n<strong>email: </strong><a href=\"mailto:ownerinq@cordilleraep.com\">ownerrelations@fourpointenergy.com</a>.</li>\r\n 	<li>If your check is stolen please contact us at:\r\n<strong>(303) 785-1581</strong>\r\n<strong>email: </strong><a href=\"mailto:ownerinq@cordilleraep.com\">ownerrelations@fourpointenergy.com</a>.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>How do I get a copy of my revenue check or joint interest billing?</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>To receive your User ID and password to <a href=\"https://www.energylink.com/\" target=\"_blank\">EnergyLink</a>, please contact us at:\r\n<strong>(303) 785-1581\r\n</strong><strong>email:</strong>  <a href=\"mailto:ownerinq@cordilleraep.com\">ownerrelations@fourpointenergy.com</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Why did you send me an IRS Form W-9?</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>The IRS requires that we confirm your Tax ID number every year and keep the <a href=\"http://fourpointenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/FourPoint_W9.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">W-9</a> on file. Please complete the form using the name provided on your revenue check, and your Social Security number or Tax ID number.</li>\r\n</ul>','FAQ','','inherit','closed','closed','','514-revision-v1','','','2016-06-13 21:14:59','2016-06-13 21:14:59','',514,'http://fourpointenergy.com/514-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
