	(1215,2,'2016-06-13 22:31:41','2016-06-13 22:31:41','<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">At FourPoint, we believe in investing in the next generation of our future leaders. Our interns are an important part of our team. We believe in a hands-on approach to developing skills, overall growth as a professional, and preparation for what’s next following your experience. While working alongside a top-tier staff you’ll have a unique and unmatched opportunity to really understand our business as a whole while developing skills in your desired area of focus with on-the-job training. Our goal is that you are able to gain the insight needed to help guide you as you take your next steps in your career making decisions.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">Summer internships and co-opportunities during academic school years are offered to both undergraduate and graduate students throughout various departments at FourPoint:</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><a href=\"https://careers-fourpointenergy.icims.com/jobs/intro?hashed=-435679222\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"s1\">Find Internships and apply. </span></a></p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">FourPoint interns have represented the following universities:</span></p>\r\nArizona State University\r\n\r\nColorado School of Mines\r\n\r\nColorado State University\r\n\r\nDuke University\r\n\r\nMetropolitan State College of Denver\r\n\r\nUniversity of Colorado\r\n\r\nUniversity of Kansas\r\n\r\nUniversity of Wyoming\r\n\r\nWestern State University\r\n\r\nPrinceton University\r\n\r\nUniversity of Oklahoma\r\n\r\nLehigh University','Internships','','inherit','closed','closed','','227-revision-v1','','','2016-06-13 22:31:41','2016-06-13 22:31:41','',227,'http://fourpointenergy.com/227-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
